Class DtmfRecognitionConfiguration

java.lang.Object
  com.nuecho.rivr.voicexml.turn.output.interaction.DtmfRecognitionConfiguration
All Implemented Interfaces:
JsonSerializable
public final class DtmfRecognitionConfiguration
extends Object

A DtmfRecognitionConfiguration represents the DTMF part of an interaction phase recognition configuration. It is composed of a list of DTMF GrammarItem and optional properties (inter-digit timeout, term timeout, term char).
